      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  

 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-103">使用`ManualResetEvent`、 <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent>和进行线程交互(或线程信号)。<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-103">You use `ManualResetEvent`, <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent>, and <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> for thread interaction (or thread signaling).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-104">有关详细信息, 请参阅[同步基元概述](~/docs/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives.md)一文中的 "[线程交互" 或 "信号](~/docs/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives.md#thread-interaction-or-signaling)" 部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-104">For more information, see the [Thread interaction, or signaling](~/docs/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives.md#thread-interaction-or-signaling) section of the [Overview of synchronization primitives](~/docs/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives.md) article.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-105">当线程开始在其他线程继续之前必须完成的活动时, 它将调用[ManualResetEvent](xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A)以置于`ManualResetEvent`非终止状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-105">When a thread begins an activity that must complete before other threads proceed, it calls [ManualResetEvent.Reset](xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A) to put `ManualResetEvent` in the non-signaled state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-106">此线程可以被视为控制`ManualResetEvent`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-106">This thread can be thought of as controlling the `ManualResetEvent`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-107">调用[ManualResetEvent WaitOne](xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A)的线程, 等待信号。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-107">Threads that call [ManualResetEvent.WaitOne](xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A) block, awaiting the signal.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-108">控制线程完成活动后, 它将调用[ManualResetEvent](xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A) , 以指示等待线程可以继续。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-108">When the controlling thread completes the activity, it calls [ManualResetEvent.Set](xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A) to signal that the waiting threads can proceed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-109">所有等待线程都已释放。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-109">All waiting threads are released.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-110">收到信号后, 将保持`ManualResetEvent`信号, 直到通过<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset>调用方法手动重置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-110">Once it has been signaled, `ManualResetEvent` remains signaled until it is manually reset by calling the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-111">也就是说, 调用<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>会立即返回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-111">That is, calls to <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> return immediately.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-112">可以通过将布尔值传递到构造`ManualResetEvent`函数来控制的初始状态: `true`如果初始`false`状态为 "已终止", 则为; 否则为。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-112">You can control the initial state of a `ManualResetEvent` by passing a Boolean value to the constructor: `true` if the initial state is signaled, and `false` otherwise.</span></span>  
 
 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-113">`ManualResetEvent`还可与`static` <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAll%2A>和<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAny%2A>方法一起使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-113">`ManualResetEvent` can also be used with the `static` <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAll%2A> and <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAny%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-114">从 .NET Framework 版本2.0 开始, <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>派生自类。<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-114">Beginning with the .NET Framework version 2.0, <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> derives from the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-115">在<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>功能上等效<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle>于使用<xref:System.Threading.EventResetMode.ManualReset?displayProperty=nameWithType>创建的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-115">A <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> is functionally equivalent to an <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> created with <xref:System.Threading.EventResetMode.ManualReset?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-116">与类不同, 类<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle>提供对已命名的系统同步事件的访问。 <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-116">Unlike the <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> class, the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> class provides access to named system synchronization events.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-117">从 .NET Framework 版本4.0 开始, <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEventSlim?displayProperty=nameWithType>类是的轻型<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>替代项。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-117">Beginning with the .NET Framework version 4.0, the <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEventSlim?displayProperty=nameWithType> class is a lightweight alternative to <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>.</span></span>    
   
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-118">下面的示例演示如何<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>工作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-118">The following example demonstrates how <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> works.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-119">该示例以信号状态<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> ( `false`即传递给构造函数的) 开头。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-119">The example starts with a <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> in the unsignaled state (that is, `false` is passed to the constructor).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-120">该示例创建三个线程, 每个线程<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>通过调用其<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>方法, 在上被阻止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-120">The example creates three threads, each of which blocks on the <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> by calling its <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-121">当用户按**Enter**键时, 该示例调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A>方法, 该方法释放所有三个线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-121">When the user presses the **Enter** key, the example calls the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> method, which releases all three threads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-122">将此与<xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent>类的行为进行对比, 每次释放一个线程, 并在每次发布后自动重置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-122">Contrast this with the behavior of the <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> class, which releases threads one at a time, resetting automatically after each release.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-123">再次按 " **enter** " 键, 表明<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>在调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A>方法之前, 将一直保持终止状态:该示例将启动两个以上的线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-123">Pressing the **Enter** key again demonstrates that the <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> remains in the signaled state until its <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A> method is called: The example starts two more threads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-124">这些线程在调用<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>方法时不会被阻止, 而是运行到完成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-124">These threads do not block when they call the <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> method, but instead run to completion.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee071-125">再次按**enter**键将导致该示例调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A>方法, 并启动一个线程, 该线程在调用<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>时将被阻止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-125">Pressing the **Enter** key again causes the example to call the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A> method and to start one more thread, which blocks when it calls <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee071-126">按**enter**键, 最后一次调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A>以释放最后一个线程, 程序结束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee071-126">Pressing the **Enter** key one final time calls <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> to release the last thread, and the program ends.</span></span>  
  
